name: Thoughts on my mind Pt. 1 #01
description: "Thoughts on my mind Pt. 1" is something I wanted to make for some time but only now I felt I could do it. Every artwork in the serie includes my raw thoughts and emotions that I had in different situations over the last few months. They are as I wrote them. Some of the messages express things I felt then, some are still available. Take all this serie as it is. Feel free to empathise with my work and to explore a part of me. I'm grateful for all that happened. I thought I've lost myself. I was a fool. . Wish you the best. Be kind, not selfish like I was.
